Body:
I am trying to install Standalone Kaa node server I have installed all dependencies i.e., MariaDB, MongoDB, zookeeper all thirdparty components are running as services and can be seen with systemctl status <serviceNames>. But when I start Kaa service node starts and gets shutdown there are no errors But I am getting few exceptions from Kaa server Applets attached Log was obtained by this command cat * at path /var/log/kaa/
